Rainfall in an area of west central Kansas and four surrounding counties

Data for Exercise 9.8

Format

A data frame with 35 observations on the following 5 variables.

rain
a numeric vector
x1
a numeric vector
x2
a numeric vector
x3
a numeric vector
x4
a numeric vector

References

Kitchens, L. J. (2003) Basic Statistics and Data Analysis. Duxbury
